{"tid":929244,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕手殘福音] 玫瑰蘋果批","createTime":"2018-12-05T12:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:03.000Z","uid":133911,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bbf0ffc7d3a59ce280875de69bb7656ca717e0","tid":929244,"uid":133911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"嗨大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨近聖誕節，我決定暫時放低餃子，試下整甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p89NzHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp89NzHA.png&h=f39e7980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8LpBVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8LpBVW.png&h=a640293f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4CfJAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4CfJAX.png&h=edea9528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次用一個青蘋果，一半煮果醬，一半切片備用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZOFUHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZOFUHC.png&h=cc409a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨心落嘅糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izdOi9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizdOi9i.png&h=84238ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果煮完之後甜到開眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1hfJAZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1hfJAZ.png&h=dec3e544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切完片發現太厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用熱水浸咗陣先夠軟放去個酥皮度捲埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpLhcuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpLhcuk.png&h=b68f4fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將酥皮切到適合嘅大細，再碌薄佢，將煮好嘅果醬鋪上酥皮之後再放埋蘋果片，然後摺好塊酥皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjSGD9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjSGD9k.png&h=0efcad16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捲完之後都幾好樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWEt3A1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWEt3A1.png&h=870c5564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焗完之後係乾燥玫瑰花呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axCb1nH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxCb1nH.png&h=7fab5de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送多個近鏡比大家<br />\n<br />\n今次冇朋友唯有自己評<br />\n<br />\n短腿點評：<br />\n本身煮個醬果時落得太多糖，心諗仆街喇咁甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知配埋酥皮同浸水浸到冇乜味嘅蘋果嘅效果又唔錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然冇我想像中咁好食，但聖誕整嚟送比人都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次分數分兩part<br />\n味道：4/10<br />\n美觀：8/10<br />\n<br />\n後記<br />\n其實製成品嘅相其實我都send咗比好幾個朋友，但唔知點解佢哋都會有同一樣嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你用餃子皮整架？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酥皮呀係酥皮嚟架！<br />\n<br />\n其實我都好想知點解啲酥皮焗完都係一舊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92288c4b340c9faff1d8006782e6f5a83af55d85","tid":929244,"uid":114738,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"手工好撚靚 呢種濕鳩樣用黎氹女一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521963d7bef8969fc891d551a70bcf7c754a537d","tid":929244,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"嚟緊會唔會教整薑餅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843763855c96a6dabcf54ad316caab65dc2f28b3","tid":929244,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco